description: A child whose innocence and devotion set him apart from the other children of his village grows up to be one of the foremost saints of India.

title: Yaadein
description: Two young lovers set out to overcome the obstacles that stand in the way of their marriage, beginning with the objections of the girl's father.

title: Zodiac
description: A political cartoonist, a crime reporter and a pair of cops investigate San Francisco's infamous Zodiac Killer in this thriller based on a true story.

title: No Entry
description: After a prank goes sideways, three buddies find their relationships  – with women and each other – tested in unexpected ways.

title: You Carry Me
description: A soap opera producer, director and makeup artist each face wrenching family turmoil, from teen rebellion and marital infidelity to Alzheimer's.
